{"tid":24213,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"暫時減輕LIHKG食電方法：關閉背景運行","createTime":"2016-12-05T11:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-10T13:57:18.000Z","uid":3904,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b49dffc3d1d906e65c9ab180faca0d77d97dd39","tid":24213,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"LIHKG出左就嚟一星期，出post順到講wtsapp咁，相信好多巴絲打都會多左留言。但大家可能都留意到一個問題：個app好食電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/194926_686aefd75269da8fdfaf8540eea1497a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F194926_686aefd75269da8fdfaf8540eea1497a.jpg&h=48c43b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用開iPhone SE，一直出街都唔需要帶外置電，但自從裝左LIHKG 之後就要叉足兩次，而我上LIHKG同以前用HKG+上高登時間差不多。我見咁都唔係辦法（用得SE就係想輕便），然後就研究下，發現原來個app係有開background app refresh<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/195015_e0b78216fa780bd8a16aac247bcc796b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F195015_e0b78216fa780bd8a16aac247bcc796b.jpg&h=89e84355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我琴晚開始試下關左佢，個效果竟然咁驚人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S83aCZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS83aCZW.jpg&h=6c514444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今日無特別上少左LIHKG，用量基本上同平時一樣<br />\n<br />\n對於連巴，我係萬二分支持，喺你更新修正呢個問題之前，巴絲打們可以用呢個方法減輕食電問題。"},{"pid":"ca513f6291b8be3e94aeb9c83ff3941c5021ddf7","tid":24213,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:57:40.000Z","msg":"正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd2f294d3303cfae32c74ae1eb36a4836c0281e","tid":24213,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:08:18.000Z","msg":"我熄唔到背景refresh"},{"pid":"be68d9012df8590da8bc436669f2502edc6264e0","tid":24213,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2965553ef81ddac4f83d035bd874a94b2551ce","tid":24213,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"an機有無得set"},{"pid":"bee59bc0762939509ae2e2a4e34d465c0b6dcc24","tid":24213,"uid":16873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我熄唔到背景refresh</blockquote><br />\n無野了<br />\n本來就熄晒所有"},{"pid":"243f28ff3ea107c357b23010d595be0fc48f6d76","tid":24213,"uid":3332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我熄唔到背景refresh</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關ios事"},{"pid":"9c9e9eedf4d8e1df763b11c5c13f9c21b9b74184","tid":24213,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我熄唔到背景refresh</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知關唔關ios事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果開左慳電mode會無得選關<br />\n（因為慳電mode本身就關曬所有background refresh)"},{"pid":"050e85c6f7d0e7d762dc37e99fd2dc7923ec4c19","tid":24213,"uid":212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:17:14.000Z","msg":"off唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0cbd4415d248c6342adcf3cce6d3d1777c7171","tid":24213,"uid":55542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bfd4a6ac5716b34a2cab8d58293461778b70de","tid":24213,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>an機有無得set</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知<br />\n<br />\n部zenfone 借左俾人無得試<br />\n<br />\n有無an俠幫幫手？"},{"pid":"8578b3d019629b3aee9aa37a2fd70e2ded268372","tid":24213,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"